      <div class="file-item">

          <div class="file-name">文件名称</div>
          <div class="actions">
            <div class="btn-item">查看</div>
            <div class="btn-item">下载</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </template>
  </div>
</template>

<script lang="ts" setup>
import { reactive, ref } from 'vue'

let props = defineProps({
  data: {
    type: Array,
    default: () => []
  },
  fields: {
    type: Array,
    default: () => {
      ;[]
    }
  }
})

let state = reactive({
  data: [],
  show: false
})
</script>
